ug:**\n   582â†’\n   583â†’| Message                                               | Context                                            |\n   584â†’| ----------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |\n   585â†’| `[Matador] ðŸ”Œ Delayed message exchange plugin detected` | RabbitMQ delayed message plugin is available       |\n   586â†’\n   587â†’**Warn:**\n   588â†’\n   589â†’| Message                                                                   | Context                                                    |\n   590â†’| ------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |\n   591â†’| `[Matador] ðŸŸ¡ RabbitMQ delayed message exchange plugin not available...`  | RabbitMQ plugin not installed, delayed messages disabled   |\n   592â†’| `[Matador] âš ï¸ Shutdown timeout reached with N events still processing`    | Graceful shutdown timed out with pending events            |\n   593â†’| `[Matador] ðŸŸ¡ Hook onWorkerWrap threw an error`                           | The `onWorkerWrap` hook threw an exception                 |\n   594â†’| `[Matador] ðŸŸ¡ Hook loadUniversalMetadata threw an error`                  | The `loadUniversalMetadata` hook threw an exception        |\n   595â†’| `[Matador] ðŸŸ¡ Hook getQueueConcurrency threw an error`                    | The `getQueueConcurrency` hook threw an exception          |\n   596â†’| `[Matador] ðŸŸ¡ Hook getRetryDelay threw an error`                          | The `getRetryDelay` hook threw an exception                |\n   597â†’| `[Matador] ðŸŸ¡ Hook getAttempts threw an error`                            | The `getAttempts` hook threw an exception                  |\n   598â†’| `[Matador] ðŸŸ¡ Hook getMaxDeliveries threw an error`                       | The `getMaxDeliveries` hook threw an exception             |\n   599â†’| `[Matador] ðŸŸ¡ Hook {hookName} threw an error`        